quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  30,20,Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe (uMvelinqangi) ukuthi wanidala ngothuli kwase kuthi uma nina seningabantu nahlakazeka
  30,21,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe ukuthi wanidalela amakhosikazi phakathi kwenu ukuze niphumule kuwona futhi phakathi kwenu wabeka uthando nomusa, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu (nezifundo) ebantwini abacabangayo"
  30,22,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe yindalo yamazulu nomhlaba nokwehlukahlukana kwezilimi zenu kanye nemibala yenu, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu kwabafundile"
  30,23,"Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe ukulala kwenu ebusuku nasemini nokufuna kwenu ububele bakhe, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abezwayo"
  30,24,"Futhi oluye lwezimpawu zakhe ukuthi unikhombisa umbani wokwesaba nowokunika ithemba futhi wehlisela phansi amanzi (imvula) evela esibhakabhakeni bese ephilisa ngayo umhlaba emva kokufa kwawo, ngempela kulokho kunezimpawu ebantwini abanomqondo"
  30,25,Futhi olunye lwezimpawu zakhe wukuthi izulu nomhlaba kumile ngomyalelo wakhe kuyothi uma enibiza ubizo olulodwa emhlabeni bheka! Nina niyoza
  30,26,Futhi ungowakhe noma ngabe ngubani osemazulwini nasemhlabeni bonke bayamhlonipha
  30,27,"Futhi nguyena osungula indalo bese eyiphinda, futhi lokho kulula kakhulu kuyena, futhi umfanekiso wakhe uphakeme kakhulu emazulwini nasemhlabeni futhi yena uphakeme ngamandla anobuhlakani"